        <akn:num>24-531.05</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Competence treatment.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_24-531_05_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p></akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_24-531_05_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Except as provided in subsections (c) and (d) of this section, the court may order the defendant to undergo competence treatment on an inpatient basis for one or more periods of time, not to exceed 180 days in the aggregate.</akn:p></akn:content>
